        <h2>üìß Email Infrastructure</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>smtplib</strong> - SMTP email protocol implementation</li>
            <li><strong>email.mime</strong> - Email message formatting (text, multipart)</li>
            <li><strong>Gmail SMTP Server</strong> - Email delivery service
                <ul>
