        <h2>üèóÔ∏è Architecture Pattern</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Monolithic Application</strong> - Single Streamlit app</li>
            <li><strong>Session-based State</strong> - No database required for MVP</li>
            <li><strong>Synchronous Processing</strong> - Real-time content generation</li>
            <li><strong>Direct SMTP</strong> - No email service abstraction</li>
        </ul>

